While Canada uses a similar type of reactor, it has abundant supplies of uranium and so has

00:14:18.200 --> 00:14:24.280
had much less incentive to put much effort into thorium fuel. How would a thorium fuel cycle work in

00:14:24.280 --> 00:14:31.160
India? The basic fuel cycle would work as follows. Uranium cycle fast-breeder reactors would produce

00:14:31.160 --> 00:14:36.840
